{"text_id":191684,"tokens":["The"," use"," of"," FAC","S"," technology"," in"," classrooms"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," how"," teachers"," and"," students"," interact"," and"," respond"," to"," one"," another","\u2019","s"," emotions","."," FAC","S","\u2014","an"," acronym"," for"," Facial"," Action"," Coding"," System","\u2014","is"," a"," tool"," for"," decoding"," and"," recognizing"," emotions"," based"," on"," facial"," expressions","."," Using"," this"," technology",","," teachers"," and"," students"," alike"," can"," quickly"," recognize",","," interpret",","," and"," react"," positively"," to"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," emotions",".","\n","For"," teachers",","," this"," technology"," can"," provide"," insight"," into"," not"," only"," a"," student","'","s"," emotions"," but"," also"," their"," cognitive"," state","."," For"," instance",","," FAC","S"," allows"," teachers"," to"," gauge"," a"," student","\u2019","s"," understanding"," and"," engagement"," with"," a"," topic"," in"," a"," way"," that"," would"," otherwise"," be"," impossible","."," It"," also"," helps"," teachers"," detect"," signs"," of"," distress"," or"," dis","engagement"," in"," the"," classroom",","," allowing"," them"," to"," offer"," assistance"," to"," the"," struggling"," student"," before"," the"," behavior"," has"," the"," opportunity"," to"," become"," too"," disruptive","."," Implementing"," FAC","S"," technology"," in"," classrooms"," can"," furthermore"," help"," identify"," patterns"," of"," anxiety",","," frustration",","," and"," other"," stress","-","related"," behavior"," that"," may"," originate"," from"," outside"," the"," classroom",".","\n","For"," students",","," FAC","S"," technology"," can"," help"," recognize"," their"," own"," emotions"," and"," develop"," a"," deeper"," understanding"," of"," them","."," This"," not"," only"," improves"," their"," social"," and"," emotional"," skills",","," providing"," them"," with"," the"," building"," blocks"," for"," responding"," appropriately"," to"," their"," own"," and"," other"," people","\u2019","s"," emotions",","," but"," also"," boosts"," their"," overall"," academic"," performance","."," Beyond"," that",","," FAC","S"," technology"," can"," help"," foster"," an"," environment"," of"," respect"," and"," understanding"," between"," teachers"," and"," students","."," By"," having"," a"," visual"," representation"," of"," emotional"," states",","," both"," teachers"," and"," students"," can"," more"," effectively"," communicate"," and"," resolve"," issues"," within"," the"," classroom",".","\n","In"," summary",","," FAC","S"," technology"," in"," classrooms"," serves"," a"," valuable"," resource"," to"," both"," teachers"," and"," students","."," Not"," only"," does"," it"," improve"," a"," student","\u2019","s"," social"," and"," emotional"," intelligence",","," it"," also"," provides"," teachers"," with"," an"," effective"," tool"," to"," better"," monitor"," and"," respond"," to"," a"," student","\u2019","s"," emotions"," in"," an"," appropriate"," manner","."," Given"," the"," many"," potential"," benefits"," of"," FAC","S"," technology",","," its"," use"," in"," classrooms"," should"," be"," strongly"," considered"," as"," a"," means"," of"," improving"," both"," education"," and"," social"," interaction"," between"," teachers"," and"," students","."," ","\n\n\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," effective"," tools"," for"," educators"," is"," the"," Facial"," Action"," Coding"," System"," (","FAC","S",")."," This"," technology"," helps"," teachers"," and"," students"," better"," detect"," and"," respond"," to"," emotions",","," providing"," numerous"," benefits"," for"," both"," parties","."," First",","," it"," helps"," teachers"," gain"," insight"," into"," their"," student","'","s"," emotions"," and"," cognitive"," state","."," This"," allows"," them"," to"," spot"," signs"," of"," distress"," or"," dis","engagement"," in"," the"," classroom",","," enabling"," them"," to"," offer"," assistance"," before"," the"," behavior"," spirals"," out"," of"," control","."," For"," students",","," FAC","S"," allows"," them"," to"," recognize"," and"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," emotions",","," equipping"," them"," with"," the"," understanding"," and"," reaction"," skills"," necessary"," to"," behave"," appropriately",".","\n","Moreover",","," FAC","S"," technology"," can"," help"," teachers"," and"," students"," develop"," an"," environment"," rich"," in"," mutual"," respect"," and"," understanding","."," Access"," to"," visual"," representations"," of"," emotional"," states"," promotes"," more"," efficient"," communication"," and"," resolution"," of"," issues"," between"," educators"," and"," students","."," This"," in"," turn"," helps"," improve"," overall"," academic"," performance",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," use"," of"," FAC","S"," technology"," in"," the"," classroom"," is"," a"," beneficial"," tool"," for"," both"," teachers"," and"," students"," alike","."," Not"," only"," does"," it"," equip"," students"," with"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," their"," emotions",","," it"," also"," gives"," teachers"," an"," invaluable"," resource"," to"," detect"," and"," respond"," to"," their"," student","\u2019","s"," emotions"," in"," a"," timely"," manner","."," As"," a"," result",","," the"," implementation"," of"," FAC","S"," technology"," should"," be"," considered"," as"," a"," viable"," option"," for"," improving"," both"," education"," and"," social"," interaction"," between"," teachers"," and"," students","."," It"," is"," truly"," a"," powerful"," tool"," that"," should"," not"," be"," overlooked","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}